Distance: 1650 Conditions: Variable headwind conditions on the course (10-20mph). Strong tail current. Comments: Times should not be compared as crews were starting with a floating start. In the second boat race, crews started about a length past the line. In the B5 race, Andover and Belmont Hill combined to make a composite entry.
Thank you to all crews for making the drive to Andover.

None
